<div
  style="background:#0077BD; padding:15px; border-radius:8px; color:#fff; text-align:center; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"
>
  <h1>Welcome to Devify, {{name}}!</h1>
</div>
<div style="padding:15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color:#333;">
  <p>Thank you for signing up with Devify. Please verify your email address by
    clicking the button below:</p>
  <p style="text-align:center; margin:20px 0;">
    <a
      href="{{verificationLink}}"
      style="background:#0077BD; color:#fff; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none;"
    >Verify Email</a>
  </p>
  <p>If you did not create an account, you can ignore this message.</p>
</div>